    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2>因过去的星际大战而衰退已久的「惑星阿尔卡迪亚」。在再次快要取回安宁的世界里突然暴走的古代兵器「守护者」。主人公「栞音・奥布西迪亚斯三等空尉」驱使高机动飞行机甲「战姬」，开始了镇压守护者的任务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这个概念</strong></h2>美少女×SF军事题材。本作品有涉及15000字以上的冒险部分，以及玩家和Boss都是由高解像度的可爱SD绘图，优美并且能够活动的栩栩如生可以说是最强组合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/03840a43b3ee8b274dc62740ada702ca.poster.avif?t=1577073427\" width=550 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/03840a43b3ee8b274dc62740ada702ca.webm?t=1577073427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏系统</strong></h2>・保留原本的射击游戏要素，还增添了新的要素。<br><br><br>・沿袭搭载了以保险和选项，低速模式和擦弹而闻名的同人射击游戏的系统。在低速模式，机关枪和加农炮可进行同时射击使威力up。<br><br>・采用在射击游戏里并不常见的HP制。被敌人发射的子弹射中也能承受数发。还可以使用道具恢复。<br><br><br>・普通射击会扩散，距离敌人越远威力会越弱。然后越早打倒敌人就会掉落成绩道具。如何持续战斗是提高成绩的窍门。<br><br>・完全支持由手柄的游戏杆操作，可以像操作FPS的精细视点一样操作玩家，使近距离的躲弹更加容易。<br><br>・使用保险时会有可爱的特写动画演出。觉得多余？不，你可能会因为能够每次看到主人公可爱的特写而欢呼雀跃吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色</h2><br><strong>栞音・奥布西迪亚斯</strong><br><br>原本是孤儿拥有在孤儿院被抚养的过去。以歼灭自律兵器为夙愿申请配属专门讨伐自律兵器的99独立空战中队后入队。三等空尉。巨乳。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/03840a43b3ee8b274dc62740ada702ca.poster.avif?t=1577073427\" width=550 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/03840a43b3ee8b274dc62740ada702ca.webm?t=1577073427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>琉璃・克里洛登德鲁姆</strong><br><br>暗视栞音为好对手，但栞音完全没察觉。近战能力在军队里也是数一数二。与年龄相比身心偏幼被大家所喜爱。贫乳。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/b7ef2ff8fb682c3be625e1fbbff43654.poster.avif?t=1577073427\" width=550 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/b7ef2ff8fb682c3be625e1fbbff43654.webm?t=1577073427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>月 胡蝶</strong><br><br>打倒自律兵器回收部件的赏金猎人。在亚人里也拥有超高的膂力，重武装也能轻松操作。爆乳。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/be493472cabfa760b5635482de6c5e55.poster.avif?t=1577073427\" width=550 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/be493472cabfa760b5635482de6c5e55.webm?t=1577073427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>莉可莉丝</strong><br><br>天空都市的人工生命体不擅长战斗某种程度上能操纵自律兵器。贫乳。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/781e2feecc32f469db15b02416f34691.poster.avif?t=1577073427\" width=550 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/781e2feecc32f469db15b02416f34691.webm?t=1577073427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>艾丽斯</strong><br><br>在与机甲匹配性很高的人工生命体中拥有更高的匹配性。 在教会内所器重。巨乳。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/54692f519d50d4fa77d2195e35b1df0c.poster.avif?t=1577073427\" width=550 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070110/extras/54692f519d50d4fa77d2195e35b1df0c.webm?t=1577073427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
